  "title": "ISic003554. An antiquarian 'forgery'",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σκρειβωνία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σκρειβωνία\"><span data-text=\"Σκρειβωνία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Σκριβωνία\">Σκρειβωνία</span></span></span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"ζῶσα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ζῶσα</span>  <span data-text=\"ἑαυτῇ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἑαυτοῦ\">ἑαυτῇ</span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ἐποίησεν</span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"καί\">καὶ</span>  <span data-text=\"τοῖς\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">τοῖς</span>  <span data-text=\"ἰδίοις\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ἴδιος\">ἰδίοις</span>  <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"πᾶσιν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"πᾶς\">πᾶσιν</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Σκρειβωνία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Σκριβωνία\">Σκρειβωνία</span>  <span data-text=\"ζῶσα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ζῶσα</span>  <span data-text=\"ἑαυτῇ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἑαυτοῦ\">ἑαυτῇ</span>  <span data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ἐποίησεν</span>  <span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"καί\">καὶ</span>  <span data-text=\"τοῖς\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">τοῖς</span>  <span data-text=\"ἰδίοις\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ἴδιος\">ἰδίοις</span>  <span data-text=\"πᾶσιν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"πᾶς\">πᾶσιν</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σκρειβωνία\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σκρειβωνία\"><span data-text=\"Σκρειβωνία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Σκριβωνία\">ΣΚΡΕΙΒΩΝΙΑ</span></span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"ζῶσα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΖΩΣΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἑαυτῇ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἑαυτοῦ\">ΕΑΥΤΗ</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΕΝ</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"καί\">ΚΑΙ</span><span data-text=\"τοῖς\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ΤΟΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἰδίοις\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ἴδιος\">ΙΔΙΟΙΣ</span><br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-text=\"πᾶσιν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"πᾶς\">ΠΑΣΙΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Σκρειβωνία\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Σκριβωνία\">ΣΚΡΕΙΒΩΝΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"ζῶσα\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΖΩΣΑ</span><span data-text=\"ἑαυτῇ\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἑαυτοῦ\">ΕΑΥΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"ἐποίησεν\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"ποιέω\">ΕΠΟΙΗΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"καὶ\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"καί\">ΚΑΙ</span><span data-text=\"τοῖς\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"ὁ\">ΤΟΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἰδίοις\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"ἴδιος\">ΙΔΙΟΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"πᾶσιν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"πᾶς\">ΠΑΣΙΝ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic003554_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003554_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic003554.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic003554-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after comparison of Kaibel, Filippi and SEG, prioritising Kaibel's transcription of the manuscript tradition</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>As Korhonen lucidly details, the inscription is one of a series of late 18th century local antiquarian forgeries, constructed on the basis of existing texts, principally those to be found in the 1769 first edition of the corpus of Torremuzza. Kaibel classed the entire series already as forgeries in IG XIV.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 52.0899 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">21*</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Filippi 2002 74-75 no. 5/15 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001991\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001991</a>  </li><li> Filippi 2005 65 no.5/14 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002296\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002296</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2017 198 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001484\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001484</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
